name: Mickey 17
summary: The highly anticipated film "Mickey 17" is set to hit theaters soon, as revealed by the recently released trailer. Directed by Academy Award-winning Bong Joon-ho, the sci-fi comedy stars Robert Pattinson as Mickey, a man who can't seem to stop dying. The trailer has generated excitement among fans, with many praising Pattinson's voiceover and the film's quirky and mysterious atmosphere. The movie follows Mickey, an expendable crew member on a mission to colonize a distant planet, who is constantly replaced with a new clone whenever he dies. As Mickey goes through countless deaths, he begins to question his purpose and individuality. With its intriguing premise and acclaimed director, "Mickey 17" is sure to captivate audiences when it is finally released.

name: Toto' Schillaci
summary: Salvatore Schillaci, the renowned Italian footballer who played a crucial role in Italy's 1990 FIFA World Cup triumph, has passed away at the age of 59 after battling colon cancer. Nicknamed "Toto," Schillaci's impressive performance during the World Cup earned him the Golden Boot and the Bronze Ball awards. He also had a notable career at Juventus and Internazionale during the 1980s and 1990s. Schillaci's exceptional skills and influential presence on the field have solidified his legacy as an Italian football icon. Tributes and condolences have poured in from around the world, honoring his contributions to the sport and his memorable contribution to Italy's World Cup victory.
